<h1>.publishAdd( <code>{id}</code>,<code>attribute</code>, <code>idAdded</code>, [<code>request</code>], [<code>options</code>] )</h1>
<h3>Purpose</h3>
<p>Publishes a notification when an associated record is added to a model's collection.  For example, if a <code>User</code> model has an association with the <code>Pet</code> model so that a user can have one or more pets available in its <code>pets</code> attribute, then any time a new pet is associated with a user <code>publishAdd</code> may be called.</p>
